cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to manipulate the sentiment of a text while preserving its semantics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses disentangled representations, which are a popular topic in machine learning and deep learning research, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which are common in the fields of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Neural Networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper also mentions the analysis of trajectories in embedding space, which is a technique commonly used in Computer Vision (cs.CV).
